00:00:01.114 --> 00:00:04.680
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:00:10.881 --> 00:00:17.814
At the very outset we have to know that truth is what it is.

00:00:24.148 --> 00:00:29.747
We cannot change it, we cannot conceptualise it,

00:00:30.514 --> 00:00:35.248
at this human state.

00:00:47.614 --> 00:00:51.614
Whatever I want to tell you today,

00:00:52.014 --> 00:00:56.248
you are not to accept it blindfolded,

00:01:03.447 --> 00:01:08.047
but you should have an open mind of a scientist

00:01:13.248 --> 00:01:20.248
and if it works, then you have to accept, as honest people,

00:01:25.747 --> 00:01:31.214
because it is for the benevolence of every individual

00:01:33.413 --> 00:01:38.248
and for the benevolence of your country

00:01:38.480 --> 00:01:42.248
and for the benevolence of the whole world.

00:01:51.148 --> 00:01:55.248
These are special times when we are born.

00:01:59.047 --> 00:02:01.148
I call it as a blossom time,

00:02:03.514 --> 00:02:07.248
where many seekers of truth are born,

00:02:10.814 --> 00:02:14.781
but they have to know first of all, what is the truth.

00:02:20.081 --> 00:02:27.181
First thing is that you are not this body, this mind,

00:02:27.647 --> 00:02:31.514
this intelligence, this ego, these conditionings,

00:02:31.747 --> 00:02:34.947
but you are the pure Spirit.

00:02:49.148 --> 00:02:53.614
The second truth is that there is a subtle,

00:02:53.814 --> 00:02:57.914
all-pervading power of divine love

00:03:05.014 --> 00:03:09.148
and this power does all the living work.

00:03:12.914 --> 00:03:17.547
We see these beautiful flowers and we take them for granted.

00:03:17.881 --> 00:03:21.248
We don’t even think that it’s a miracle,

00:03:27.547 --> 00:03:31.680
how from one seed these flowers have come.

00:03:37.847 --> 00:03:41.647
Also who runs our heart?

00:03:45.747 --> 00:03:48.814
Doctors will say, autonomous nervous system,

00:03:52.347 --> 00:03:54.347
But who is this 'auto'?

00:03:56.614 --> 00:04:04.014
We have science but it cannot give us answers fully.

00:04:09.947 --> 00:04:14.847
It cannot answer, why are we here on this earth.

00:04:19.280 --> 00:04:23.447
It cannot answer what is our purpose of life.

00:04:27.914 --> 00:04:31.148
It cannot tell you about totality.

00:04:34.248 --> 00:04:36.747
So we take to religion.

00:04:39.881 --> 00:04:44.248
It’s very disappointing to see that all these great religions

00:04:44.447 --> 00:04:48.413
are only power oriented or money oriented,

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:57.914
and they are not spirit oriented.

00:05:02.248 --> 00:05:07.413
Every religion, every scripture has said that,

00:05:07.647 --> 00:05:10.747
you are to be born again.

00:05:16.280 --> 00:05:19.714
They have talked of your resurrection.

00:05:24.014 --> 00:05:28.181
Some people just brand themselves as born again but they are not.

00:05:33.248 --> 00:05:35.248
They are just like us.

00:05:37.714 --> 00:05:41.747
Any religion, now for example Catholic religion we can take:

00:05:46.714 --> 00:05:51.680
It is absolutely unnatural to make nuns and

00:05:51.914 --> 00:05:54.547
priests who cannot marry.

00:06:00.680 --> 00:06:02.747
That’s why there are problems.

00:06:04.847 --> 00:06:10.747
They are priests, they are nuns, but they are having women

00:06:11.014 --> 00:06:14.248
and the nuns are becoming pregnant.

00:06:21.747 --> 00:06:26.547
It is also true that when we are not

00:06:26.747 --> 00:06:30.580
connected with this all-pervading power,

00:06:30.814 --> 00:06:38.214
we are slaves of all sorts of ideologies.

