is having people who are committing suicides,

00:12:23.148 --> 00:12:27.380
And other Scandinavian countries who are affluent again,

00:12:27.580 --> 00:12:30.881
are competing with them in committing suicide.

00:12:38.747 --> 00:12:43.347
All this is happening, we see it every day in the newspaper

00:12:43.547 --> 00:12:45.547
and we are shocked.

00:12:50.413 --> 00:12:55.047
What is the reason, we should find out, what is the solution.

00:13:00.313 --> 00:13:08.114
The main problem is that we are not yet fully evolved.

00:13:13.847 --> 00:13:18.148
We have not yet become the Spirit.

00:13:21.914 --> 00:13:27.781
In our evolutionary state we have become human beings, all right,

00:13:32.413 --> 00:13:38.847
but there has to be something more, the last break through,

00:13:43.280 --> 00:13:48.181
by which we get our wisdom

00:13:52.380 --> 00:13:57.248
and we relate it to reality.

00:14:02.248 --> 00:14:06.248
So as you are told, this subtle system

00:14:06.347 --> 00:14:10.347
is within you which works it out.

00:14:16.248 --> 00:14:19.547
It’s within all of you.

00:14:22.347 --> 00:14:29.547
It was placed in the triangular bone, which we call as sacrum.

00:14:33.680 --> 00:14:36.747
That means the Greek knew it’s a sacred bone.

00:14:41.914 --> 00:14:48.413
So there is already placed within us a power by which we can ascend

00:14:48.614 --> 00:14:52.248
and become one with this all-pervading power.

00:14:59.847 --> 00:15:06.313
Now in the west the whole civilization has grown big, very big.

00:15:10.714 --> 00:15:15.480
But for this big tree we should know our roots.

00:15:21.413 --> 00:15:25.081
And the knowledge of the roots if it comes from East,

00:15:25.248 --> 00:15:27.313
why should we mind?

00:15:32.347 --> 00:15:38.714
For a saint, East and West doesn’t exist.

00:15:43.947 --> 00:15:48.547
The solution lies in understanding what we are,

00:15:52.413 --> 00:15:56.614
and that is very simple, very easy to get it.

00:16:00.148 --> 00:16:03.680
Sahaja, means born with you,

00:16:07.680 --> 00:16:11.781
is the right to have this yoga,

00:16:11.981 --> 00:16:18.914
meaning the union with this all-pervading power of divine love.

00:16:27.714 --> 00:16:29.747
Like this instrument here,

00:16:29.947 --> 00:16:32.847
if it is not connected to the mains it has no meaning.

00:16:33.047 --> 00:16:35.114
It has no identity.

00:16:43.747 --> 00:16:49.480
In these modern times even to talk about God is out of date,

00:16:54.580 --> 00:16:59.514
but now the time has come to prove the existence of God!

00:17:03.747 --> 00:17:06.514
Sahaja Yoga is meta science,

00:17:09.380 --> 00:17:14.647
where, when you get connected with this all-pervading power,

00:17:14.847 --> 00:17:20.114
you can feel the absolute truth on your fingertips.

00:17:28.547 --> 00:17:32.248
Even children can feel the same,

00:17:35.413 --> 00:17:39.680
because Spirit is the source of absolute truth.

00:17:45.614 --> 00:17:49.248
You have been already told there are five, six and seven centres

00:17:49.347 --> 00:17:55.280
on the right and five, six and seven centres on the left hand.

00:18:03.313 --> 00:18:06.881
These are sympathetic centres which get enlightened.

00:18:10.981 --> 00:18:15.547
When this power rises through six centres,

00:18:15.747 --> 00:18:19.580
She emerges through your seventh here,

00:18:19.781 --> 00:18:23.714
centre which we call as the fontanel bone area

00:18:32.981 --> 00:18:39.847
and you get actualisation. Again I say actualisation of baptism.

00:18:43.480 --> 00:18:46.680
It is not that somebody puts the water on your head

00:18:46.881 --> 00:18:48.881
and says you are baptised.

00:18:53.014 --> 00:18:57.847
There is no difference between a Christian, Hindu, Muslim, anyone,

00:19:02.680 --> 00:19:06.547
they can commit the same sins.

00:19:09.947 --> 00:19:13.647
But once this connection takes place,

00:19:17.447 --> 00:19:20.047
you start feeling on your fingertips

00:19:20.248 --> 00:19:23.514
the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost, as they call it.

00:19:29.480 --> 00:19:35.547
Then you know also what’s wrong with you.

00:19:41.514 --> 00:19:45.413
Most of the world problems are because of human beings.

00:19:49.680 --> 00:19:55.148
And most of the human problems are because of their subtle centres,

00:20:00.881 --> 00:20:06.248
because these centres look after your

00:20:06.413 --> 00:20:11.047
physical, mental, emotional and spiritual being,

00:20:22.480 --> 00:20:28.480
and if you know what’s wrong with you on your fingertips,

00:20:28.680 --> 00:20:32.814
you have the self knowledge of your being.

00:20:39.081 --> 00:20:44.181
That means instead of going to the moon, you go within yourself.

00:20:50.647 --> 00:20:55.914
Now as a result your physical being is cured,

00:20:56.114 --> 00:21:02.114
means many of the incurable diseases have been cured by Sahaja Yoga.

00:21:11.413 --> 00:21:17.680
Also mental troubles and spiritual troubles which have come

00:21:17.881 --> 00:21:23.847
by going to wrong places - all have been mostly cured.

00:21:32.881 --> 00:21:36.814
All this curing takes place by your own power

00:21:42.647 --> 00:21:48.614
and it’s your own doing, your own understanding

00:21:48.814 --> 00:21:51.514
which gives you this Self-realization.

00:21:57.680 --> 00:21:59.747
Then the second thing that happens to you,

00:21:59.947 --> 00:22:04.248
that on your fingertips you can feel the centres of others.

00:22:09.947 --> 00:22:12.614
Say, if you think of somebody who is dead

00:22:12.814 --> 00:22:16.248
or somebody who is far away and just put your hands like this,

00:22:16.480 --> 00:22:19.947
you can know what centres are in jeopardy.

00:22:30.747 --> 00:22:35.447
Thus you develop a new dimension in your human awareness

00:22:35.680 --> 00:22:39.114
which you call as 'collective consciousness'.

00:22:46.647 --> 00:22:52.248
Now, when we are thinking,

00:22:52.447 --> 00:22:56.814
we are thinking about the past or about the future.

00:23:01.881 --> 00:23:05.480
Past is finished and future doesn’t exist.

00:23:09.881 --> 00:23:16.747
So, if I say you have to be in the present you cannot be.

00:23:21.447 --> 00:23:26.347
But when this power rises, She separates these thoughts

00:23:29.514 --> 00:23:34.248
and between those thoughts there is a space

00:23:36.981 --> 00:23:40.313
and this space is the present.

00:23:42.847 --> 00:23:47.847
So you develop another dimension in your human awareness,

00:23:48.047 --> 00:23:52.614
which we call as 'thoughtless aware',

00:23:55.714 --> 00:23:58.014
'thoughtless awareness'.

00:24:04.781 --> 00:24:07.347
That means you are aware, absolutely alert,

00:24:10.248 --> 00:24:12.280
but you are thoughtless.

00:24:13.614 --> 00:24:16.047
If you want to think, you can think,

00:24:16.248 --> 00:24:19.047
if you don’t want to think, you need not think.

00:24:24.747 --> 00:24:30.047
Because of this bombardment of thoughts you get stress and strain.

00:24:35.280 --> 00:24:38.413
But then you open out

00:24:40.248 --> 00:24:45.847
and all problems are sort of dissolved.

00:24:49.447 --> 00:24:54.313
For example, if you are in the water, you are afraid of the waves.

00:24:58.747 --> 00:25:05.248
But somehow if you can get into the boat then you can see the waves,

00:25:09.547 --> 00:25:11.647
you are not disturbed by them.

00:25:13.081 --> 00:25:18.248
But somehow if you learn how to go back jump into the water

00:25:18.413 --> 00:25:21.447
and swim, you can save many.

00:25:27.947 --> 00:25:30.413
This is how Sahaja Yoga works.

00:25:32.714 --> 00:25:35.947
One person gets his realization,

00:25:36.148 --> 00:25:39.881
they get the power to give realizations to others.

00:25:45.814 --> 00:25:50.847
Like one candle is enlightened, can enlighten many candles.

00:25:54.881 --> 00:25:58.847
So this is the purpose of our life

00:26:01.148 --> 00:26:06.480
and the destiny is that we enter into the Kingdom of God.

00:26:12.014 --> 00:26:15.114
The life is filled with blessings there,

00:26:18.447 --> 00:26:20.680
you are completely protected,

00:26:22.714 --> 00:26:25.447
you enjoy every moment of your life

00:26:28.248 --> 00:26:33.614
and suddenly you find all over the world you have lots of friends,

00:26:33.814 --> 00:26:37.248
your own relations.

00:26:44.280 --> 00:26:51.647
Because Spirit is the source of absolute knowledge,

00:26:56.714 --> 00:26:59.114
absolute truth.

00:27:02.081 --> 00:27:07.248
In the light of the Spirit you understand

00:27:07.447 --> 00:27:11.114
what is right and what is wrong for you.

00:27:17.114 --> 00:27:19.114
I don’t have to tell you.

00:27:21.781 --> 00:27:28.181
For example I am holding on to a snake and there is darkness,

00:27:33.248 --> 00:27:36.447
and somebody will say, "It's a snake, you throw away!"

00:27:36.647 --> 00:27:42.280
I will say, "No, it is a rope", because I am obstinate.

00:27:51.047 --> 00:27:54.014
'Till the snake bites me, I’ll not give up.

00:27:57.614 --> 00:28:01.081
But supposing there is little light,

00:28:03.814 --> 00:28:06.181
immediately I’ll throw away.

00:28:08.714 --> 00:28:11.114
That light, when it comes into you,

00:28:11.313 --> 00:28:13.313
you know what is constructive for you

00:28:13.514 --> 00:28:15.747
and what is destructive for you,

00:28:21.214 --> 00:28:25.047
and effortlessly you get transformed.

00:28:31.148 --> 00:28:36.248
The Spirit, when enlightens your attention,

00:28:36.447 --> 00:28:39.047
the attention becomes active.

00:28:44.480 --> 00:28:48.647
Suddenly you find your attention has become innocent.

00:28:52.514 --> 00:28:57.747
Believe me, innocence cannot be destroyed, whatever you may try.

00:29:02.047 --> 00:29:04.380
Maybe there may be some clouds,

00:29:07.047 --> 00:29:10.248
but these clouds, once removed,

00:29:10.480 --> 00:29:14.148
you find your innocence completely intact,

00:29:19.647 --> 00:29:23.947
and your attention becomes absolutely innocent.

00:29:28.313 --> 00:29:30.714
Such attention is so powerful

00:29:30.914 --> 00:29:34.514
that wherever you put the attention, things work out.

00:29:43.447 --> 00:29:46.480
It is benevolent,

00:29:47.914 --> 00:29:49.914
it is compassionate

00:29:51.181 --> 00:29:53.814
and it’s very intelligent.

00:29:56.881 --> 00:30:00.114
The Spirit is the source of joy.

00:30:03.148 --> 00:30:08.947
Joy is not happiness and unhappiness. It is absolute.

00:30:13.547 --> 00:30:18.347
In this state of joy, you become the witness.

00:30:22.014 --> 00:30:24.781
The whole thing looks like a drama

00:30:28.914 --> 00:30:36.680
and you enjoy your own spiritual powers.

00:30:41.881 --> 00:30:45.647
Then you don’t develop your ego,

00:30:48.081 --> 00:30:52.181
because you start talking in third person.

00:30:55.413 --> 00:30:57.413
For a Sahaja Yogi will say,

00:30:57.614 --> 00:31:00.580
“Mother, it’s not working, it’s not going."

00:31:00.781 --> 00:31:03.347
They won’t say, “I can’t do it.”

00:31:10.914 --> 00:31:12.947
Thus you become an angel.

00:31:15.248 --> 00:31:18.480
It all sounds very fantastic, I agree,

00:31:21.214 --> 00:31:23.214
but you are fantastic!

00:31:24.680 --> 00:31:26.981
You are glorious!

00:31:28.114 --> 00:31:30.148
You don’t know yourself.

00:31:31.181 --> 00:31:35.580
Once you know yourself you'll be amazed.

00:31:39.148 --> 00:31:44.413
Only thing, you have to not blindly refuse me

00:31:44.614 --> 00:31:47.248
or to blindly accept me.

00:31:54.081 --> 00:32:00.114
The only problem is that I cannot force Sahaja Yoga on you.

00:32:04.413 --> 00:32:06.413
I respect your freedom.

00:32:08.413 --> 00:32:10.413
You have to ask for it

00:32:12.313 --> 00:32:17.148
and if you have the pure desire, it works.

00:32:20.313 --> 00:32:23.248
It works in every one.

00:32:25.547 --> 00:32:30.313
Also there’s a big fashion to feel guilty for nothing at all.

00:32:34.480 --> 00:32:36.814
Now if you have done any mistakes

00:32:37.014 --> 00:32:39.881
you just face it. Why do you feel guilty?

00:32:46.447 --> 00:32:50.947
After all you are human beings, you are not God.

00:32:54.148 --> 00:32:56.347
And to err is human.

00:32:58.081 --> 00:33:00.847
What is the use of feeling guilty?

00:33:04.081 --> 00:33:10.214
If you feel guilty then this centre
here on the left goes into problem.

00:33:16.413 --> 00:33:21.214
Physically it causes a disease called angina,

00:33:25.248 --> 00:33:31.847
also it causes you spondylitis maybe, lethargic organs,

00:33:39.547 --> 00:33:41.347
so why feel guilty.

00:33:44.014 --> 00:33:46.248
Please don’t judge yourself.

00:33:48.248 --> 00:33:50.914
This power within you will judge you.

00:33:55.248 --> 00:33:59.248
It will hardly take ten to fifteen minutes for you

00:33:59.514 --> 00:34:01.914
to get your self realisation.

00:34:07.680 --> 00:34:11.047
But you must be pleasantly placed towards yourself.

00:34:13.881 --> 00:34:16.947
Not to condemn yourself for anything what so ever.

00:34:20.014 --> 00:34:25.248
At this moment you are perfect,

00:34:28.248 --> 00:34:31.914
because this all-pervading power of Divine love

00:34:32.214 --> 00:34:35.248
is the ocean of forgiveness.

00:34:40.347 --> 00:34:43.214
So you have to forgive your self fully.

00:34:45.547 --> 00:34:47.248
This is the first condition,

00:34:49.248 --> 00:34:56.114
and the second condition is that you have to forgive everyone.

00:35:00.248 --> 00:35:02.413
Logically, whether you forgive

00:35:02.647 --> 00:35:05.248
or you don’t forgive, you don’t do anything.

00:35:10.747 --> 00:35:15.480
But if you don’t forgive then you play into wrong hands

00:35:20.814 --> 00:35:24.148
and you torture yourself.

