I’ve already told you that I cannot force

01:00:06.047 --> 01:00:12.881
Divine knowledge on you, you have to ask for it.

01:00:20.248 --> 01:00:25.114
So now please take your right hand into the lower portion

01:00:25.248 --> 01:00:29.847
of your abdomen on the left hand side and ask six times,

01:00:30.114 --> 01:00:34.214
because, this centre has got six petals.

01:00:45.280 --> 01:00:49.714
“Mother please give me pure knowledge”

01:00:54.814 --> 01:00:57.747
Please say it six times.

01:01:03.214 --> 01:01:10.347
As soon as you ask for pure knowledge,

01:01:10.914 --> 01:01:15.248
the Kundalini starts rising, so we have to

01:01:15.313 --> 01:01:23.280
nourish our higher centres with our full self confidence.

01:01:43.248 --> 01:01:46.680
So now raise your right hand in the upper portion of your abdomen

01:01:46.914 --> 01:01:51.547
on the left hand side and here with full self confidence

01:01:51.814 --> 01:01:59.214
you have to say ten times, “Mother I am my own master”.

01:02:14.248 --> 01:02:20.947
I’ve already told you, that you are not this body, this mind,

01:02:21.248 --> 01:02:24.248
this ego, this intelligence, these emotions and conditionings,

01:02:24.514 --> 01:02:27.248
but you are the pure Spirit.

01:02:40.747 --> 01:02:44.248
So now raise your right hand on your heart

01:02:44.447 --> 01:02:47.647
and with full confidence please say twelve times

01:02:48.014 --> 01:02:52.347
“Mother, I am the pure Spirit”.

01:03:06.947 --> 01:03:14.447
This all-pervading divine power, is the ocean of pure knowledge.

01:03:20.480 --> 01:03:24.614
It is the ocean of compassion and bliss,

01:03:28.347 --> 01:03:32.313
but above all it is the ocean of forgiveness.

01:03:37.047 --> 01:03:41.047
So whatever mistakes you might have committed get easily dissolved

01:03:41.248 --> 01:03:45.081
into this ocean of forgiveness.

01:03:53.647 --> 01:03:59.447
So now raise your right hand in the corner of your shoulder

01:03:59.747 --> 01:04:03.547
and your neck and turn your head to your right.

01:04:09.747 --> 01:04:12.081
Now forgive your self

01:04:13.647 --> 01:04:21.447
and with self full confidence please say it sixteen times.

01:04:21.881 --> 01:04:27.248
“Mother I am not guilty at all”.

01:04:40.647 --> 01:04:45.480
I’ve already explained to you that whether

01:04:45.747 --> 01:04:50.280
