01:07:18.413 --> 01:07:24.248
On the fontanel bone area which was the soft bone in your childhood.

01:07:35.248 --> 01:07:39.248
Now please put down your head,

01:07:41.814 --> 01:07:43.914
here again I cannot force

01:07:44.148 --> 01:07:47.547
self-realisation on you. You have to ask for it.

01:07:53.480 --> 01:07:56.447
So press your scalp, push back your fingers,

